# Graphify-first (ontology L3 memory)

```bash
npm run graph:query -- "<question>"
npm run graph:path -- "A" "B"
npm run graph:explain -- "concept"
npm run graph:update
```

Respect `.graphifyignore` (no repomix, no vendor skill packs).  
Canonical wiki: `graphify-out/wiki/index.md` only if navigating **one** page after query.

Forbidden: dump `GRAPH_REPORT.md`, bulk wiki, recreate archives.
